item.title: Help with editing run/compile so it works for me
item.dc:creator: @Cali_Tree Cali Tree
item.description:
@Cali_Tree wrote:

Right click on Run and the Compiler and go to edit. Copy and paste what you get with each one labeled with what it goes to. Plus put what JDK you have.
